scenes.description: Tsunomaki Watame, Shishiro Botan, and Ouro Kronii perform 'What an amazing swing'.
Mori Calliope, Koseki Bijou, Ichijou Ririka, and Akai Haato perform '未来島' (Miraijima / Future Island).
Houshou Marine, Minato Aqua, Nekomata Okayu, and IRyS perform 'I I I'.
